data.description: Welcome to 5458 Newfield Ave ~ Come see this cute brick 3/1.5 well maintained cape cod ~ It's bigger than it looks with lots of great features ~ Basement updated partially finished with dry bar ~ New windows approx 2003 ~New gas HVAC approx 2016 ~ New roof approx 2008 ~ on dead end street ~ Don't miss out on the gem ~ call for your private showing today! Sold as is.
